  "2026-05-23T10:18:38.759Z",release-flow-subagent,"release-flow-subagent start: read-only inspection of scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs and changelog/release-note helpers; goal is to identify changelog_unreleased_empty skip path, commit inspection since last tag, and minimal loud/visible implementation. No file edits planned."
  "2026-05-23T10:19:29.544Z",release-test-docs-subagent,"Final findings (release-test/docs, read-only): Existing coverage: tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts covers package release scripts, auto-release workflow strings, changelog promotion, help output, and delegated verify-published checks; tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts covers release/auto-release workflow gate wiring; tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts only checks release script/path markers including changelog_unreleased_empty. Gap: no behavioral regression proves run-release-pipeline treats release-relevant commits + empty CHANGELOG [Unreleased] as loud/actionable instead of quiet ok skipped:true reason=changelog_unreleased_empty. Smallest test update: add focused case in tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts, preferably against an extracted/exported pure classifier from scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs so it does not need a temp git repo or full gates. Assert src/docs release-relevant files + nonzero commits + empty unreleased returns the new warning/failure/actionable reason, while .agents/pm-only changes still skip cleanly. Keep existing changelog promotion test unchanged. Docs/changelog: docs/RELEASING.md Automated Daily Driver should explicitly say release-relevant commits require a populated [Unreleased] entry and empty [Unreleased] is an actionable release-prep failure/warning, not a silent success; CHANGELOG.md [Unreleased] should get one concise Changed/Fixed entry for pm-ot8r when implementation lands. Focused verification commands: PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts; pnpm quality:docs-skills; node scripts/check-secrets.mjs; after a clean tree, node scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs --dry-run --json --telemetry-mode off --skip-compatibility --skip-telemetry-sentry."
  "2026-05-23T10:19:48.862Z",release-flow-subagent,"release-flow-subagent findings: current baseline skip path is run-release-pipeline.mjs getLastTag/getCommitCountSince/getChangedFilesSince -> filter !.agents/pm -> readUnreleasedChangelogBody -> changelog_unreleased_empty. In committed baseline that path returns ok:true/skipped:true even with src-touching files. Current worktree already has an uncommitted minimal patch exporting isChangelogRequiredPath/buildEmptyChangelogResult and making empty changelog return ok:false + warning + exit 1 when package/source/workflow/release-script files changed. Suggested tests: unit import of buildEmptyChangelogResult for src vs docs-only; integration/temp git repo proving --json exits nonzero with source file + empty Unreleased; tracker-only remains ok:true tracker_only_changes_since_last_tag; changelog-promote empty section remains failing."
  "2026-05-23T10:20:13.648Z",privacy-observability-subagent,"Final privacy/observability review: no accidental literal private host/key/token leak found in tracked release/telemetry/Sentry docs/scripts. Evidence: node scripts/check-secrets.mjs => 'No credential-like secrets detected in tracked files.'; strict secret regex over tracked release/telemetry/Sentry docs/scripts only matched scripts/release/utils.mjs argv variable name 'token', not a secret value; private ops path check showed git ls-files scripts/prod => no tracked files and git check-ignore maps scripts/prod/telemetry/* to .gitignore:24. Notable tracked references are env/secret placeholders only (SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN, SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN, NPM_TOKEN, GH_TOKEN) in docs/workflows. Current post-implementation observability verification commands to run: pnpm release:gates -- --telemetry-mode required --max-sentry-critical 10 --max-sentry-high 20 --max-telemetry-error-rate 6 --max-telemetry-missing-error-rows 0 --json; or direct node scripts/release/sentry-telemetry-gate.mjs --json --telemetry-mode required --max-critical 10 --max-high 20 --max-telemetry-error-rate 6 --max-telemetry-missing-error-rows 0; plus node scripts/check-secrets.mjs after release docs/workflow edits. For CI parity, auto-release uses telemetry_mode off by default unless workflow_dispatch overrides it, while release.yml runs Sentry issue gate with telemetry-mode off and thresholds 10/20."
  "2026-05-23T10:22:43.974Z",codex-release-ux,"Evidence: Implemented loud empty-changelog release guard.  now exports classifier helpers, keeps tracker/docs-only empty [Unreleased] skips green, and exits nonzero with  plus  when source/package/script/workflow files changed. Verification passed: focused release automation spec 9/9; \n> @unbrained/pm-cli@2026.5.23 build [local-path-redacted]\n> node scripts/prepare-build-cache.mjs && tsc -p tsconfig.json && node scripts/finalize-build.mjs; \n> @unbrained/pm-cli@2026.5.23 quality:docs-skills [local-path-redacted]\n> node scripts/release/docs-skills-gate.mjs\n\nDocs/skills gate passed.; No credential-like secrets detected in tracked files.; linked ok: true\nid: \"pm-ot8r\"\ntests:\n  - command: \"node scripts/check-secrets.mjs\"\n    scope: \"project\"\n    timeout_seconds: 120\n    note: \"tracked secret scan after release/docs changes\"\n  - command: \"PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts\"\n    scope: \"project\"\n    timeout_seconds: 240\n    note: \"focused release automation regression tests\"\n  - command: \"pnpm build\"\n    scope: \"project\"\n    timeout_seconds: 240\n    note: \"full TypeScript build after release pipeline script export changes\"\nrun_results:\n  - command: \"node scripts/check-secrets.mjs\"\n    status: \"passed\"\n    exit_code: 0\n    execution_context:\n      requested_pm_context_mode: \"schema\"\n      pm_context_mode: \"schema\"\n      auto_pm_context_applied: false\n      is_pm_command: false\n      is_pm_tracker_read_command: false\n      source_project_pm_path: \"[local-path-redacted]/.agents/pm\"\n      sandbox_project_pm_path: \"/tmp/pm-linked-test-mW5AHs/schema/project/.agents/pm\"\n      source_global_pm_path: \"[local-path-redacted]\"\n      sandbox_global_pm_path: \"/tmp/pm-linked-test-mW5AHs/schema/global\"\n      source_project_item_count: 829\n      sandbox_project_item_count: 0\n      source_globa